  <div class= "col-md-3 col-xs-12">
  <div class="panel panel-success">
      <div class="panel-heading">What are follow limits?</div>
      <div class="panel-body">Pithugram has follow and update limits for stability and abuse control.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class= "col-md-3 col-xs-12">
    <div class="panel panel-danger">
      <div class="panel-heading">How do I find people to follow?</div>
      <div class="panel-body">When you create an account, you can search for people by name or @username.
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>



